A bar scam involves scammers

414
00:35:04,580 --> 00:35:06,460
posing as friends

415
00:35:06,460 --> 00:35:08,900
and tricking them
into buying overpriced drinks.

416
00:35:09,240 --> 00:35:10,780
Please stay alert

417
00:35:10,780 --> 00:35:12,460
that this behavior is illegal.

418
00:35:12,460 --> 00:35:14,780
In severe cases,
it may even be considered a crime.

419
00:35:23,270 --> 00:35:28,120
♪Wear a smile to hide sorrow♪

420
00:35:30,760 --> 00:35:35,920
♪Everyone's life is a tale of weariness♪

421
00:35:38,360 --> 00:35:44,860
♪Tears that won't flow,
dust that won't clear♪

422
00:35:45,480 --> 00:35:50,670
♪Every story has its imperfections♪

423
00:35:53,420 --> 00:35:58,210
♪Chasing the wind,
soaring high without regrets♪

424
00:36:00,810 --> 00:36:05,890
♪In the end, earning an invisible trophy♪

425
00:36:08,350 --> 00:36:14,590
♪Living freely, living purely♪

426
00:36:15,090 --> 00:36:20,630
♪Life is but a dance of asking and giving♪

427
00:36:23,390 --> 00:36:29,960
♪If you face it bravely,
there's no need for shame♪

428
00:36:29,960 --> 00:36:35,960
♪Everyone has their own shining moment♪

429
00:36:38,300 --> 00:36:44,850
♪The scenery is intriguing,
but the end is the same♪

430
00:36:45,250 --> 00:36:51,260
♪Waiting is truly precious♪

431
00:36:53,290 --> 00:36:59,980
♪Face it bravely,
and regrets will naturally fade♪

432
00:37:00,160 --> 00:37:05,860
♪Embrace the gifts of time♪

433
00:37:08,360 --> 00:37:14,900
♪Why not journey together
through the ups and downs?♪

434
00:37:15,400 --> 00:37:20,650
♪Together, enjoy
the gentle breeze and soft clouds♪
